Copy-Sync-Paste
===============

Copy-Sync-paste is a tool to seamlessly synchronize clipboard across devices.

Presently, works between a Linux PC and android devices.

Steps to use :
------------

1) Install the .apk file ( CopySyncPasteServer/bin/CopySyncPasteServer.apk ) in the android device. 
2) Run the client ( CopySyncPasteClient/csp_client.py )from the PC to sync the PC's clipboard contents to mobile device.
